Love Island - Series 3, Episode 46




Three of the couples go on epic final dates. Chris and Olivia board a super yacht, Kem and Amber get the red carpet treatment and Jamie and Camilla enjoy some alone time with musical accompaniment. Elsewhere, Alex and Montana talk about their feelings for each another, while Marcel enlists Camilla's help as he prepares a romantic gesture for Gabby. The islanders prepare some show-stopping performances for the Love Island Talent Show 2017.
